### 1. AUTHENTICATION (AUTH)

### Login with Success
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@fieldops.com",
  "password": "strongpassword123"
}

### Login with Error
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@fieldops.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 2. SERVICE ORDERS

### Create OS
POST http://localhost:3000/service-orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "client_name": "ACME Corp",
  "address": "123 Industrial Way",
  "description": "Preventive maintenance on HVAC system",
  "technician_id": "tech-uuid-456",
  "priority": "high"
}

### List OS
GET http://localhost:3000/service-orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Alter Status (To In Progress)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/service-orders/os-999/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "in_progress"
}

### 3. VALIDATIONS (Finalization Rules)

### Finalize without checklist -> error
PATCH http://localhost:3000/service-orders/os-999/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### Finalize without photos -> error
PATCH http://localhost:3000/service-orders/os-999/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### Finalize without signature -> error
PATCH http://localhost:3000/service-orders/os-999/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### Finalize correctly -> sucesso
PATCH http://localhost:3000/service-orders/os-999/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### 4. RBAC (Role-Based Access Control)

### Técnico tentando acessar OS de outro -> erro
GET http://localhost:3000/service-orders/os-from-another-tech
Authorization: Bearer {{technician_token}}

### Supervisor acessando equipe -> sucesso
GET http://localhost:3000/service-orders/team-member-os
Authorization: Bearer {{supervisor_token}}
